rows.label: qst702502_msg0001
rows.name:
Monsters suddenly
attacked from the port!

rows.label: qst702502_msg0002
rows.name:
Most of our fighters are out right
now, so I was worried, but now that
Adel-sama is here, we're safe.

rows.label: qst702502_msg0003
rows.name:
Leave the watch here to me! I'll
let you know if anything happens!

rows.label: qst702502_msg0101
rows.name:
Now monsters have appeared
from the other side!

rows.label: qst702502_msg0102
rows.name:
They're not the kind you
usually see around here.
Where did they come from...?

rows.label: qst702502_msg0201
rows.name:
More monsters appeared and
they got in so quickly...

rows.label: qst702502_msg0202
rows.name:
Most of the evacuation is done, so
all that's left is to defeat them!

rows.label: qst702502_msg0203
rows.name:
Adel-sama, just a little
more! I believe in you!
